    <p>Players won't want to miss out on the chance to trigger the special Epic Rewards bonus. Once this feature is activated, players must collect six hat icons. It's like going through Alice's adventures in Wonderland all over again! The waiting game is certainly worth it, though. Once the respin feature ends, players will be awarded an extra multiplier that can help them secure the jackpot of their dreams. Who needs a rabbit hole when you can win big with Alice Riches?</p>"
}

{
