    "content": "<p>Ah, Alice Riches. What can we say about the graphics in this game? Well, for starters, we can say that they're pretty darn cool. This slot game takes the classic story of Alice in Wonderland and throws in a bit of punk rock and futuristic style. You'll see all of your favorite characters as you've never seen them before.</p>

