    <p>All in all, the graphics in Alice Riches are spot on. They capture the essence of the story perfectly while also bringing something new and unique to the table. So if you're looking to play a slot game that's easy on the eyes (and we're not just talking about the payouts), then Alice Riches is definitely worth a spin.</p>"
}

{
